description: Gets a Routing Rule with the specified Rule name within the specified Front Door.

message.description: Error message indicating why the operation failed.

subscription_id.description: The subscription credentials which uniquely identify the Microsoft Azure subscription. The subscription ID forms part of the URI for every service call.

resource_group_name.description: Name of the Resource group within the Azure subscription.

front_door_name.description: Name of the Front Door which is globally unique.

routing_rule_name.description: Name of the Routing Rule which is unique within the Front Door.
